Chubais was Deputy Prime Minister. There was a default. Chubais was a power engineer, everyone learned the words "fanning shutdown" and "blackout". Chubais was responsible for the development of science. He had a lot of money, but science did not have it. Now Chubais is the president's special envoy for the development of international relations. And that's all you need to know to answer the question "Will there be a war?"